subsection.def:
INLS Certificate (INLS證書) means a certificate issued under regulation 24(1)(b);
                        (L.N. 92 of
                2018)

noxious liquid substance (有毒液體物質) has the same meaning as in Annex II;
                        (L.N. 92 of
                2018)

sea
                    (海、海域)
                includes all waters navigable by sea-going ships;

subsection.content:
If an intermediate survey of the ship has been carried out by reference to an
                anniversary date, the annual survey of the ship by reference to the anniversary date
                for the relevant year is not required to be carried out. (L.N. 92 of 2018)
